snippet.title: Pangya United: Golf MMORPG Nise Official HD game trailer - PC
snippet.description:
http://www.gamezplay.org - Players also have the opportunity to gear up with the Deadly Stapler Club Set, Monogatari Comet and Shinobu Oshino, the cute but deadly vampire Mascot -- all distinctive items befitting the "Nisemonogatari" story.

The new "Nisemonogatari" items allow players to add an eclectic flair to their in-game characters in Panyga -- the anime-themed casual golf MMORPG.
